                        <p class="fw-bold mb-1">₱2,999.00 / month / location</p>
                        <p>3 users (₱500.00/additional user)</p>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-4">Email/Viber chat support</p>

                        <h5 class="text-start mb-3">Features</h5>
                        <ul class="text-start small list-unstyled">
                            <li>✔ Dashboard, Vehicle Management, Estimates</li>
                            <li>✔ Job Orders, Invoices, Appointments</li>
                            <li>✔ Customer & Supplier Management</li>
                            <li>✔ Accounting (Chart of Accounts, P&L, Balance Sheet)</li>
                            <li>✔ Reports (Sales, Service, Mechanic, Top Products)</li>
                            <li>✔ 50 Free SMS/month</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="fw-bold mt-3">One-time implementation fee of ₱20,000.00</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ELITE PLAN -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm border-primary position-relative">
                    <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-50 translate-middle">
                        <span class="badge bg-primary">Popular</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                        <h3 class="h4 text-warning mb-3">ELITE</h3>
                        <p class="fw-bold mb-1">₱3,999.00 / month / location</p>
                        <p>5 users (₱500.00/additional user)</p>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-4">Email/Viber chat support</p>

                        <h5 class="text-start mb-3">Includes all STANDARD features plus:</h5>
                        <ul class="text-start small list-unstyled">
                            <li>✔ 100 Free SMS/month & Custom Sender ID</li>
                            <li>✔ Automated SMS Service Reminders</li>
                            <li>✔ Loyalty and Memberships</li>
                            <li>✔ Barcoding & Online Payments (Future)</li>
                            <li>✔ Supplier & Customer Portals (Future)</li>
                            <li>✔ Stock Transfer & Inventory Forecasting (Future)</li>
                            <li>✔ Payroll (Future), BIR CAS</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="fw-bold mt-3">One-time implementation fee of ₱30,000.00</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ENTERPRISE PLAN -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                        <h3 class="h4 text-success mb-3">ENTERPRISE</h3>
                        <p class="fw-bold mb-1">Custom Pricing</p>
                        <p>Minimum of 10 branches</p>
                        <p>10 users (₱300.00/additional user)</p>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-4">Email/Viber chat/Phone support</p>

                        <h5 class="text-start mb-3">Includes all ELITE features plus:</h5>
                        <ul class="text-start small list-unstyled">
                            <li>✔ Dedicated Server Instance</li>
                            <li>✔ Customized Printout & Inspection Templates</li>
                            <li>✔ Customized Software Branding</li>
                            <li>✔ Multi-Location Management & Reports</li>
                            <li>✔ API Access</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="fw-bold mt-3">Call us for customized pricing</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Additional Features Section -->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Additional Features</h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-primary me-3 fs-4"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="h5">Security & Compliance</h4>
                        <p>Enterprise-grade security with data encryption, role-based access control, and compliance with industry standards.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                    <i class="bi bi-phone text-primary me-3 fs-4"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="h5">Mobile Access</h4>
                        <p>Access your projects on the go with our mobile-friendly interface and native mobile apps.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                    <i class="bi bi-clock-history text-primary me-3 fs-4"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="h5">Time Tracking</h4>
                        <p>Track time spent on tasks and projects with our integrated time tracking feature.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                    <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text text-primary me-3 fs-4"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="h5">Reporting</h4>
                        <p>Generate comprehensive reports and insights to make informed decisions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
